      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-add-spi-000      thru vis-add-spi-999        .
           perform   vis-add-spi-des-000  thru vis-add-spi-des-999    .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Tipo addebito spese bollo                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-add-spb-000      thru vis-add-spb-999        .
           perform   vis-add-spb-des-000  thru vis-add-spb-des-999    .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Data scadenza manuale pagamento                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-pag-dsm-000      thru vis-pag-dsm-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Ammontare quota a forfait pagamento             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-pag-qaf-000      thru vis-pag-qaf-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Ammontare acconto                               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-pag-act-000      thru vis-pag-act-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita pagina 3                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     vis-tes-reg-999.
       vis-tes-reg-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione prompts testata                           *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       pmt-tes-reg-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Erase linee impegnate dalla testata a seconda   *
      *              * del numero pagina                               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "EL"                 to   v-ope                  .
           if        w-cnt-sts-imp-npt    =    1
                     move 07              to   v-lin
           else      move 04              to   v-lin                  .
           move      21                   to   v-lto                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Deviazione in funzione del numero pagina        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     pmt-tes-reg-100
                     pmt-tes-reg-200
                     pmt-tes-reg-300
                     depending            on   w-cnt-sts-imp-npt      .
           go to     pmt-tes-reg-999.
       pmt-tes-reg-100.
      *              *=================================================*
      *              * Pagina 1                                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Tipo archivio                                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-tip-arc-000      thru pmt-tip-arc-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Partita iva cliente o fornitore                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-piv-cof-000      thru pmt-piv-cof-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Codice dipendenza                               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-dpz-arc-000      thru pmt-dpz-arc-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Si/no documento 'xml'                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-snx-sdi-000      thru pmt-snx-sdi-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Nome documento 'xml'                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-fil-sdi-000      thru pmt-fil-sdi-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Data documento del fornitore                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-dat-doc-000      thru pmt-dat-doc-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Numero documento del fornitore                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-num-doc-000      thru pmt-num-doc-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita pagina 1                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     pmt-tes-reg-999.
       pmt-tes-reg-200.
      *              *=================================================*
      *              * Pagina 2                                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Inoltro pagamenti                               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-inl-pgt-000      thru pmt-inl-pgt-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Sigla valuta per fatturazione                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-sgl-vpf-000      thru pmt-sgl-vpf-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Assoggettamento iva                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-ass-iva-000      thru pmt-ass-iva-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Contropartita acquisti                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-ctp-acq-000      thru pmt-ctp-acq-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Importo documento in valuta                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-iiv-doc-000      thru pmt-iiv-doc-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Importo documento in valuta base                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-imp-doc-000      thru pmt-imp-doc-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Data riferimento per CGE                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-dri-mgd-000      thru pmt-dri-mgd-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Numero riferimento per CGE                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-nri-mgd-000      thru pmt-nri-mgd-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita pagina 2                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     pmt-tes-reg-999.
       pmt-tes-reg-300.
      *              *=================================================*
      *              * Pagina 3                                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Codice forma di pagamento                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-cod-fop-000      thru pmt-cod-fop-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Percentuale sconto pagamento                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-scp-aap-000      thru pmt-scp-aap-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Appoggio pagamento al fornitore                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-app-pgf-000      thru pmt-app-pgf-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Tipo addebito spese incasso                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-add-spi-000      thru pmt-add-spi-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Tipo addebito spese bollo                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-add-spb-000      thru pmt-add-spb-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
