      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-ccp-app-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se campo da visualizzare                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-app-pgf (1)    not  = 03
                     go to vis-ccp-app-999.
